<!-- Content -->
<div class="container my-5">
    <h1 class="mb-4">Our Sustainability Commitment</h1>
    <p>At shaktiride, we understand our responsibility towards the planet. That’s why we have implemented eco-friendly initiatives to reduce our carbon footprint and promote a greener future. From electric vehicles to efficient route planning, sustainability is at the heart of everything we do.</p>
    <h3 class="mt-4">Key Sustainable Practices</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Switching to electric and hybrid vehicles</li>
        <li>Reducing fuel consumption through smart routing</li>
        <li>Partnering with local environmental organizations</li>
        <li>Encouraging ride-sharing to lower emissions</li>
    </ul>
    <p>We believe small steps can create big change, and with your support, devCab is helping build a cleaner, healthier future for everyone.</p>
</div>

